column5: Hey All,  There was a great article about this adventure in the Canadian FlyFisher. Check it out....  http://nomadsoftheseas.com/
Any trip that has "Incredible" in it means I can't afford it   Looks amazing though.  You go, and tell us how it went
I am thinking that the board should sponser me to go so that I can give us all an informed opinion.
i'll tell ya about another INCREDIBLE fly in fishing lodge.....  http://www.halleyscamps.com/destinations/l...ttle-falls.html    Hawk
